----
+ __SCP-5990__
[[div class="pseudocrumbs"]]
[[[scp-series-6|SCP Series VI]]] >> SCP-5990
[[/div]]
----
[[/div]]

[[div class="modal"]]
[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Aflopstyle-dark/alt_logo_bw.png class="icon-tint" style="height: 100px; width: 100px; padding: 1rem"]]
[[div class="scp-header"]]
= **__SCP Database Entry__**
[[/div]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:flops-header
|item=5990
|containment=keter
|level=4
|security=secret
